WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.560
Standart og‘ish tushunchasini yaxshilab eslab 
qolish uchun bir nechta yakuniy gap.

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:08.970
Birinchidan, turli guruhlarning tarqalishini 
taqqoslash va ichidan eng tarqoqini aniqlash 

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:13.590
uchun standart og‘ish tez-tez ishlatiladi.

00:00:13.590 --> 00:00:18.295
Ikkinchidan, ma’lumotlar moliya 
yoki iqtisodga tegishli bo‘lsa,

00:00:18.295 --> 00:00:22.625
yuqori standart og‘ish yuqori xavfga 
ega bo‘lish bilan bog‘liq.

00:00:22.625 --> 00:00:24.610
Aksiyalar narxlarini taqqoslashda,

00:00:24.610 --> 00:00:29.380
Vaqt o‘tishi bilan yuqori standart og‘ish 
bilan o‘zgaradigan birja narxi 

00:00:29.380 --> 00:00:35.220
standart past og‘ish bilan o‘zgarib turadigan 
aksiyalar narxiga nisbatan xavfli.

00:00:35.220 --> 00:00:37.230
Uchinchidan, taqqoslash adolatli bo‘lishi uchun,

00:00:37.230 --> 00:00:40.330
barcha ma’lumotlar bir xil 
birliklarda bo‘lishi kerak.

00:00:40.330 --> 00:00:42.945
Agar bitta ma’lumot to‘plamida 
dollar o‘lchov birligini ishlatsangiz,

00:00:42.945 --> 00:00:44.675
boshqasida esa evro, unda

00:00:44.675 --> 00:00:49.520
ushbu ma’lumotlar to‘plamlarini qay biri 
tarqoqrog‘ligini aniqlash uchun solishtirish noto‘g‘ri.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:55.120
Va nihoyat, o‘zgaruvchanlik o‘lchov birligi sizning 
dastlabki o‘lchovlaringizning kvadrati bo‘ladi.

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:58.950
Masalan, agar daromadni dollar 
bilan o‘lchagan bo‘lsangiz,

00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:02.040
o‘zgaruvchanlik AQSh dollar kvadrati 
birligida bo‘ladi,

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:04.470
bu esa unchalik foydali emas.

00:01:04.470 --> 00:01:07.410
Shuning uchun standart og‘ish,

00:01:07.410 --> 00:01:09.510
yani ixtilofning kvadrat ildizi,

00:01:09.510 --> 00:01:12.330
o‘lchash uchun foydaliroq hisoblanadi

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:16.655
chunki u asl ma’lumotlar to‘plamining 
o‘lchov birligida hisoblanadi.

00:01:16.655 --> 00:01:19.055
Agar daromadni dollar bilan o‘lchasangiz,

00:01:19.055 --> 00:01:23.000
standart og‘ish ham dollar o‘lchov birligiga ega.

